OL,3,C150 job cuts at hospital trust would
OL,4,Cbe a 'catastrophe,' warns staff member
OL,6,FThe Royal Cornwall Hospitals Trust is
OL,7,Fproposing 150 job cuts in its
OL,8,Fadministrative roles.
OL,10,FThe Trust is in charge of Royal
OL,11,FCornwall Hospital, St Michael's
OL,12,FHospital, West Cornwall Hospital and
OL,13,FSt Austell Surgical Hub.
OL,15,FAn anonymous staff member at the Royal
OL,16,FCornwall Hospital told ITV West
OL,17,FCountry that the changes would be a
OL,18,F"catastrophe" that would lead to
OL,19,Fincreased stress on staff.
