OL,3,C150 job cuts at hospital trust would
OL,4,Cbe a 'catastrophe,' warns staff member
OL,6,F"As the only major hospital for the
OL,7,Fwhole of Cornwall, we cannot afford to
OL,8,Flose so many staff. Services will
OL,9,Ffail, the workload will not decrease
OL,10,Fso less staff doing more work will
OL,11,Flead to more stress, higher sickness
OL,12,Flevels and patient care will be
OL,13,Fcompromised."
OL,15,FThe staff member said the cuts would
OL,16,Faffect "staff who are the backbone and
OL,17,Finsturmental in being at the front of
OL,18,Fensuring needs are met and services
OL,19,Fare performing well."
