OL,3,C150 job cuts at hospital trust would
OL,4,Cbe a 'catastrophe,' warns staff member
OL,6,FUnison: cuts "deeply worrying for
OL,7,Fstaff and patients"
OL,9,FA member of the public who said they
OL,10,Fwere connected with someone affected
OL,11,Fby the situation told ITV West Country
OL,12,Fthat "staff have been left shocked and
OL,13,Ffloundering."
OL,15,FStephen Timms, the union UNISON's
OL,16,FCornwall Acute health branch secretary
OL,17,Fdescribed the plans as "deeply
OL,18,Fworrying for both staff and patients."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
