OL,3,C150 job cuts at hospital trust would
OL,4,Cbe a 'catastrophe,' warns staff member
OL,6,F"Cutting a quarter of all
OL,7,Fadministrative roles could have
OL,8,Fserious consequences for patient
OL,9,Fsafety and care.
OL,11,F"The Trust's own risk assessment
OL,12,Facknowledges that referrals could be
OL,13,Fmissed and that follow-up care may
OL,14,Fsuffer. Services are already under
OL,15,Fhuge strain, this proposal feels
OL,16,Frushed and short-sighted," the union
OL,17,Fsaid.
