OL,3,C150 job cuts at hospital trust would
OL,4,Cbe a 'catastrophe,' warns staff member
OL,6,F"Healthcare in Cornwall faces unique
OL,7,Fpressures, an ageing local population,
OL,8,Fintense winter demand, and a surge in
OL,9,Fvisitors over the summer. Cornwall's
OL,10,Fhealth system needs additional
OL,11,Finvestment, not fewer staff.
OL,13,F"The Trust says it will try to
OL,14,Fredeploy affected workers, but with a
OL,15,Frecruitment freeze in place and no
OL,16,Fvacancies across local NHS or council
OL,17,Fservices, it's hard to see how that's
OL,18,Fpossible. Staff are anxious about
OL,19,Ftheir futures, and rightly so."
