OL,3,C150 job cuts at hospital trust would
OL,4,Cbe a 'catastrophe,' warns staff member
OL,6,FUNISON said it continues to challenge
OL,7,Fthe plans and has called for a rethink.
OL,9,FRoyal Cornwall Hospitals Trust: "We
OL,10,Frecognise for many it is an anxious
OL,11,Ftime"
OL,13,FRoyal Cornwall Hospitals Trust
OL,14,Fconfirmed its consulting with staff on
OL,15,Fcuts, saying the proposals would not
OL,16,Fonly benefit patients but also "better
OL,17,Fstructured and more rewarding roles,
OL,18,Fimproved career pathways... and
OL,19,F(would) free up time for clinicians."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
