OL,3,C150 job cuts at hospital trust would
OL,4,Cbe a 'catastrophe,' warns staff member
OL,6,F"We recognise for many it is an
OL,7,Fanxious time," the Trust wrote. "We
OL,8,Fare encouraging everyone to share
OL,9,Ftheir views and ideas throughout the
OL,10,Fconsultation period, so that we can
OL,11,Fshape the final proposals together."
OL,13,F"Our priority will be to find
OL,14,Fopportunities through vacancies across
OL,15,FRCHT and our NHS partners, to retain
OL,16,Fskilled and experienced colleagues
OL,17,Fwherever possible," it added.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
