OL,3,C150 job cuts at hospital trust would
OL,4,Cbe a 'catastrophe,' warns staff member
OL,6,F"We are supporting colleagues
OL,7,Fthroughout the consultation period,
OL,8,Foffering many ways to provide feedback
OL,9,Fand influence the final proposals, as
OL,10,Fwell as providing practical and
OL,11,Femotional support through face-to-face
OL,12,Fservice, online programmes and our
OL,13,Fstaff networks."
OL,15,FAccording to the Trust, there is
OL,16,Fcurrently the need to make savings of
OL,17,Fnearly #50 million.
