OL,3,C150 job cuts at hospital trust would
OL,4,Cbe a 'catastrophe,' warns staff member
OL,6,FInspectors from the Care Quality
OL,7,FCommission (CQC) said patients were at
OL,8,F"risk of unsafe treatment" at Royal
OL,9,FCornwall Hospital.
OL,11,FAt the time, the Trust said says it
OL,12,Ffully accepted the recommendations of
OL,13,Fthe report and has worked to improve
OL,14,Fissues such as ambulance handovers.
